          <li><strong>Financial Fraud:</strong> Voice cloning to impersonate executives for fraudulent transactions</li>
          <li><strong>Personal Harassment:</strong> Creating fake content to damage reputations or blackmail individuals
          </li>
          <li><strong>Undermining Trust:</strong> Eroding public confidence in visual and audio evidence</li>
        </ul>
        <p>As technology advances, these threats continue to evolve, requiring better detection tools and public
          awareness.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="learn-card">
