          <li><strong>Biological Signals:</strong> Checking for natural pulse, breathing patterns, and blinking</li>
          <li><strong>Facial Inconsistencies:</strong> Identifying unnatural facial movements or expressions</li>
          <li><strong>AI Pattern Recognition:</strong> Using neural networks trained to spot manipulation artifacts</li>
          <li><strong>Metadata Analysis:</strong> Examining file information for signs of editing or generation</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Our detection system combines these techniques to provide comprehensive analysis of suspected deepfakes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="learn-card">
